              borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(UIConstants.radiusM),
            ),
            child: Icon(icon, color: color, size: compact ? 18 : 22),
          ),
          SizedBox(
            height: compact ? UIConstants.spacingS : UIConstants.spacingM,
